title: Draft Quarto document
text:
Run analysis and get estimates!

create_model_workflow(
    parsnip::logistic_reg() %>%
        parsnip::set_engine("glm"),
    lipidomics_wide %>%
        create_recipe_spec(metabolite_cholesterol)
) %>%
    parsnip::fit(lipidomics_wide) %>%
    tidy_model_output()
